Date Posted: 2014/05/06 04:04:08Ref. JB1001843341
TellerAl Gharbia
To deliver exceptional teller services to customer via accurate and efficient processing while projecting Al-Hilal professional image in all interpersonal dealings
Skills
•	Resolve problems related to regular transactions,
technical,
customer complaints and interpersonal relations.
•	Exceed customers’ expectations in offering bank services.
•	Validate all transaction originating from the tellers and approve within delegated authority.
•	Ensure all transactions meet the bank’s policy and procedural requirements
•	Ensure daily cash and teller transaction accounts are accurately completed.
•	Hold joint custody of cash and vault keys.
•	Ensure all daily and periodic reports and reconciliation is completed in a timely and accurate manner.
•	Carry out start-of-day,
end-of-day,
and log on/off users and print all transaction reports on a daily basis.
•	Supervise all cheque clearing transactions including inward,
outward and returned cheques are handled properly in time.
•	Ensure applicable charges are debited for cheques returned.
•	Any other task entrusted by the Line Manager.
